Package blume

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Win32.Kernel32
    Java interface for Win32's kernel32 library (JNA).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ANSI
    Class for ANSI-specific prefixes and modifiers.
    Blume
    Blume implementation methods.
    BlumeColor
    Color object used by Blume for ANSI-based 8- and 24-bit coloring.
    BlumeText
    Primary Blume class for Win32 and ANSI color options and attributes.
    BlumeText.Attribute
    Standard terminal SGR (Select Graphic Rendition) display attributes.
    BlumeText.Background
    Basic color palette background color options.
    Win32
    Class built on JNA objects for Win32 console coloring.
    Win32.CONSOLE_SCREEN_BUFFER_INFO
    Java version of the native Win32 CONSOLE_SCREEN_BUFFER_INFO struct.
    Win32.COORD
    Simple console coordinate points class.
    Win32.SMALL_RECT
    Simple rectangle class.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    OSIncompatibilityException
    Blume exception thrown when a Blume operation is performed on an incompatible operating system.
